{"tid":40970,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[ios/an] Kairosoft 系列討論區","createTime":"2016-12-15T14:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T15:53:44.000Z","uid":28730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b354434abb4a4da81745ae01af19c6758c46ec7","tid":40970,"uid":28730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:03:49.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有玩pocket league story?"},{"pid":"c958a550f1393b5e918cfe852067d9c79dbc48c2","tid":40970,"uid":16093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"開羅game真係一流<br />\nKill time又好、享受育成又好、懷舊珍惜下佢格仔人都好、好似舊時玩wining3 果啲feel<br />\n<br />\n利申：全部玩晒已爆、最快果隻7年完、不過全部係An機玩、Iphone未玩<br />\n<br />\n建議上手：足球1 》冒險村》溫泉<br />\n必玩系列：冒險村、跑馬仔、合戰<br />\n最過癮唔知大家有冇玩過、有隻似外傳唔多入流、叫壽司開頭嘅、經營壽司店、仲要有全日本大賽咁。都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外較新嘅都要日本ac、連線同日本仔玩、都幾麻煩、例如第一款海盜、到戰隊等等、變到半單機、又要課、好似無乜癮。<br />\n<br />\n但開羅、真係值得推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"15da7e2d785a3aada0f29c7c463de24960ed3fa2","tid":40970,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻隻都玩齊，坐喺到玩5個鐘都唔攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51af16a57a2289c78e1ca70c66d9d0c80ae43c2b","tid":40970,"uid":17376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0RjH6F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0RjH6F.jpg&h=346f99cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正"},{"pid":"a921a143aa993b585515adbb2be0ce2ee644a1e6","tid":40970,"uid":42938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi