faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fbc3c6efc8464f1fe86c080fc51fe69599e0e4","tid":40970,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻進行曲好唔好玩?<br />\n上youtube 睇大陣好似好悶<br />\n淨係係咁操條女能力值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n$38 唔係幾想比<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95r4jFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95r4jFM.jpg&h=c37f4fed&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇有殘中<br />\n買左"},{"pid":"be9d358bf2d151a3c24bbe5ddc78b45366334ef2","tid":40970,"uid":15421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T06:51:16.000Z","msg":"玩過最好玩係拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177cd18a171842a3c7e2ceb44df015aff3504854","tid":40970,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"進行曲同遊戲發展國玩法差唔多<br />\n發挖人,訓練佢<br />\n能力到上限,賺錢&gt;引退"},{"pid":"992ba3d08c914650bffa8ce140a1678e6c27c048","tid":40970,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"有隻好似 冒險島. POKEMON 玩法, 幾好玩, 已爆機."},{"pid":"763de98e35f2cbd4e8a27393c8c66afafcfb59f2","tid":40970,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"溫泉後期放棄 好悶. <br />\n火車月台都係一般, <br />\n郵輪幾好玩<br />\n遊戲開發必玩. <br />\n<br />\n課金果種, 全部都失平衡. 唔掂."},{"pid":"097ee4f8ec71d0370331cc10643488f6a06c6e52","tid":40970,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫泉後期放棄 好悶. <br />\n<strong>火車月台都係一般, <br />\n郵輪幾好玩<br />\n遊戲開發必玩. </strong><br />\n<br />\n課金果種, 全部都失平衡. 唔掂.</blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"db972e455a9525356207fcd25e86af80de24c4f2","tid":40970,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:08:02.0